#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:115
msgid ""
"A produce distributor using the invoice what is delivered option sells 50 "
"heads of lettuce to a local restaurant. At the time the delivery is made, "
"only 40 heads are available. The distributor delivers the available heads of "
"lettuce and creates an invoice for what was delivered. Later, when more "
